  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>聖女エルレイン……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Saint Elraine...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>奴もエターナルソードの力を利用するつもりか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is she planning to use the power
of the Eternal Sword, too?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>奪った犯人はもちろん
エルレインにも渡せないわ、聖剣の力は</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Neither the thief who stole it, nor of course
Elraine, can be allowed to possess that
holy sword's power.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それにエルレインからは
なにか危険な力を感じる。
今ここで、奴の野望を食い止めるぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>On top of that, I can feel a dangerous power
coming from Elraine. We're going to put a
stop to her ambitions right now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
